data.description: Assumable 4.2% FHA Loan! Double AND Corner Lot! High-Quality Kitchen and Primary Bath Renovation!  Welcome to this picture-perfect craftsman bungalow, nestled on an expansive double lot. Boasting a custom kitchen, pristine primary bath, new HVAC, and fresh paint, this residence is primed for its new owners! This charming home has three well-appointed bedrooms and two tastefully designed baths, offering a comfortable and inviting living space.  The heart of the home is a spacious family room and dining area combination, graced by soaring ceilings that create an airy, open ambiance. The secondary bedrooms are generously sized, complemented by a shared hall bath that ensures convenience and functionality.  The owner’s bedroom is a private retreat, featuring a brand new, thoughtfully updated ensuite bath, providing a touch of luxury to your daily routine. The washer and dryer are conveniently located within the primary suite.  The recently renovated eat-in kitchen exudes both style and functionality, with all brand new appliances and custom stonework and finishes that elevate the space.  Throughout the home, you'll find tall ceilings and intricate heavy moldings that add a touch of sophistication and character.  Step outside onto the charming rocking chair front porch, perfect for enjoying lazy afternoons or a morning coffee.  A brand new privacy fence surrounds the property, offering an added layer of seclusion and security. This bungalow is strategically located, providing easy access to major Atlanta highways, Hartsfield-Jackson Airport, the renowned Tyler Perry Studios, and the Porsche Driving Experience Center.  Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of Atlanta's vibrant lifestyle, where classic charm meets modern convenience in a prime, accessible location. This craftsman bungalow is ready to welcome you home!
